  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 54",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "TO: Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "DATE: 9-17-47",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM: SAC, Portland",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "SUBJECT: REPORTS OF FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SECURITY MATTER - X",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Refer San Francisco letter dated September 4, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "[REDACTED], Portland, reported",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "without consulting any records that on June 24, 1947, while prospecting at a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "point in the Cascade Mountains approximately five thousand feet from sea level,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "during the afternoon he noticed a reflection, looked up, and saw a disc pro-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "ceeding in a southeasterly direction. Immediately upon sighting this object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "he placed his telescope to his eye and observed the disc for approximately",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "forty-five to sixty seconds. He remarked that it is possible for him to pick",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "up an object at a distance of ten miles with his telescope. At the time the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "disc was sighted by kr. [REDACTED] it was banking in the sun, and he observed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "five or six similar objects but only concentrated on one. He related that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "they did not fly in any particular formation and that he would estimate their",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "height to be about one thousand feet from where he was standing. He said the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "object was about thirty feet in diameter.and appeared to have a tail. It made",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "no noise.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "According to [REDACTED] he remained in the vicinity of the Cascades",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "for several days and then returned to Portland and noted an article in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "local paper which stated in effect that a man in Boise, Idaho, had sighted a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "similar object but that authorities had disclaimed any knowledge of such an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "object. He said he communicated with the Army for the sole purpose of attempt-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "ing to add credence to the story furnished by the man in Boise.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED] also related that on the occasion of his sighting the objects",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "on June 24, 1947 he had in his possession a combination compass and watch. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "noted particularly that immediately before he sighted the disc the compass",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "acted very peculiar, the hand waving from one side to the other, but that this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "condition corrected itself immediately after the discs had passed out of sight.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "Informant appeared to be a very reliable individual who advised that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "he had been a prospector in the states of Montana, Washington, and Oregon for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "the past forty years.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
